  json('[{"b58_gen1_reliability":"Widely considered BMW most reliable modern turbo engine. EngineScope 93/100. C&D 40K mile test: zero unscheduled repairs, zero oil consumption. Closed-deck block, forged crank, integrated water-to-air intercooler","ofhg_coolant_leak":"Most common B58 issue. Plastic oil filter housing combines filtration, heat exchange, coolant routing. Thermoplastic degrades under heat cycles. Fix: replace housing assembly -1500","coolant_loss":"Expansion tank cap seepage, minor hose cracks. Usually minor top-off every 10-15K mi. Monitor for rapid loss","pcv_valve_diaphragm":"SIB 01 14 23 extended warranty. Rough idle, unmetered air. Age-related, not design flaw","oil_pump_gen1":"Gen1 B58 oil pump has solid track record. Oil pump plastic adjusting ring issue affects B58TU only (2019-2022). This is the Gen1 - safe","ib_brake_recall":"NHTSA 21V-062 and 24V-104. Integrated Brake system loss of power assist, ABS, DSC. Affects all G11 7 Series. Dealer fix available","air_suspension":"Same two-axle air suspension as 750i. Rear air springs can leak at 80-120K mi. Strut replacement -3500 per corner","display_key":"Known weak point - charging issues, connectivity drops. Not critical but annoying"}]'),
